      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/russian-oil-product-cargoes-stranded-as-south-korea-cracks-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于韩国买家变得谨慎，来自俄罗斯的石油产品货物在海上不断堆积，凸显出乌克兰的入侵在两年多后仍然影响着流量。]]></description>
